#: .\ammo.json
msgid "Cute Ribbon Arrow"
msgid_plural "Cute Ribbon Arrows"
msgstr[0] "可愛緞帶箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Ribbon Arrow'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An arrow decorated with a pretty red ribbon, making them easy to find and "
"recover after battle."
msgstr "一支裝飾著漂亮紅色緞帶的箭，使它們在戰鬥後易於尋找和回收。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "Cute Feathered Arrow"
msgid_plural "Cute Feathered Arrows"
msgstr[0] "可愛羽毛箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Feathered Arrow'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An arrow decorated with the brightly coloured flight feathers of birds. "
"These are appear of exceptional craftsmanship, being lighter yet stronger "
"than standard arrows, and consequently more likely to be recovered after "
"combat since they are less likely to break."
msgstr "一支裝飾著鳥類鮮豔飛羽的箭。這些箭展現出卓越的工藝，比標準箭更輕卻更堅固，因此在戰鬥後更有可能被回收，因為它們不易折斷。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "Cute Little Mary Arrows"
msgid_plural "Cute Little Mary Arrowss"
msgstr[0] "可愛小瑪麗箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Little Mary Arrows'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"An arrow manufactured by the 'Alice & Maria' maid equipment designers. These"
" aren't arrows so much as smart projectiles, having very dense alloy cores "
"for greater force and a tip sheathed in an electromagnetic field to better "
"penetrate armor."
msgstr ""
"由'愛麗絲與瑪麗亞'女僕裝備設計師製造的箭。這些與其說是箭，不如說是智能彈體，擁有非常緻密的合金核心以提供更大力量，尖端包裹在電磁場中以更好地穿透裝甲。"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Cute Maid"
msgstr "可愛女僕"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Cute Maid"
msgstr "可愛女僕"

#. ~ Profession (male Cute Maid) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Although I worked in a large mansion, the day the cataclysm, my master's "
"family fled to a secret location I did not know of. You were alone with a "
"dirty house, and a cluttered city. It's time to go to work."
msgstr "雖然我曾在一座大宅邸工作，但在災變之日，主人的家人逃往了一個我不知道的秘密地點。你獨自面對著一座骯髒的房屋和混亂的城市。是時候開始工作了。"

#. ~ Profession (female Cute Maid) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Although I worked in a large mansion, the day the cataclysm, my master's "
"family fled to a secret location I did not know of. You were alone with a "
"dirty house, and a cluttered city. It's time to go to work."
msgstr "雖然我曾在一座大宅邸工作，但在災變之日，主人的家人逃往了一個我不知道的秘密地點。你獨自面對著一座骯髒的房屋和混亂的城市。是時候開始工作了。"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Cute Nun"
msgstr "可愛修女"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Cute Nun"
msgstr "可愛修女"

#. ~ Profession (male Cute Nun) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"After months in seculusion and prayer at our underground church, we visited "
"the surface to find the world was completely changed. There is no need for "
"despair, for God is with us."
msgstr "在我們地下教堂隱居祈禱數月後，我們來到地表，發現世界已徹底改變。無需絕望，因為上帝與我們同在。"

#. ~ Profession (female Cute Nun) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"After months in seculusion and prayer at our underground church, we visited "
"the surface to find the world was completely changed. There is no need for "
"despair, for God is with us."
msgstr "在我們地下教堂隱居祈禱數月後，我們來到地表，發現世界已徹底改變。無需絕望，因為上帝與我們同在。"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Cute Schoolgirl"
msgstr "可愛女學生"

#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Cute Schoolgirl"
msgstr "可愛女學生"

#. ~ Profession (male Cute Schoolgirl) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"I used to think it would be nice if school closed forever. Now that the "
"cataclysm has happened, it seems my wish has come true."
msgstr "我曾以為學校永遠關閉會是件好事。現在災變發生了，似乎我的願望成真了。"

#. ~ Profession (female Cute Schoolgirl) description
#: .\classes.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"I used to think it would be nice if school closed forever. Now that the "
"cataclysm has happened, it seems my wish has come true."
msgstr "我曾以為學校永遠關閉會是件好事。現在災變發生了，似乎我的願望成真了。"

#: .\item_category.json
msgid "KAWAII CATEGORY"
msgstr "KAWAII 類別"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Cute Maid Clothes"
msgid_plural "Cute Maid Clothess"
msgstr[0] "可愛女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Maid Clothes'}
#: .\items.json
msgid "Made out of the hopes and dreams of men."
msgstr "由男人的希望與夢想製成。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (summer form)"
msgid_plural "Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (summer form)s"
msgstr[0] "可愛女僕高級制服（夏季形態）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (summer form)'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "Add thermal lining"
msgstr "添加保暖襯裡"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (summer form)'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "You modify the maid outfit to better protect against the cold."
msgstr "你修改了女僕裝以更好地抵禦寒冷。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (summer form)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (winter form)'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"Centuries of maid sewing techniques have culminated in this pinnacle of maid"
" outfit technology: a year-round outfit that can be transformed to fit any "
"weather or season."
msgstr "數個世紀的女僕縫紉技術最終成就了這項女僕裝技術的巔峰：一套全年適用的服裝，可變換以適應任何天氣或季節。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (winter form)"
msgid_plural "Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (winter form)s"
msgstr[0] "可愛女僕高級制服（冬季形態）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (winter form)'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "Remove thermal lining"
msgstr "移除保暖襯裡"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Cute Maid Adv. Uniform (winter form)'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "You modify the maid outfit to better protect against the heat."
msgstr "你修改了女僕裝以更好地抵禦炎熱。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO"
msgid_plural "Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PROs"
msgstr[0] "可愛女僕制服 LSS-PRO"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "You activate the uniform's climate control."
msgstr "你激活了制服的氣候控制系統。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO'}.
#: .\items.json
msgid "The uniform does not have enough power left."
msgstr "制服剩餘電量不足。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO (on)'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"The standard maid uniform may not be enough to survive in this dangerous new"
" world. This improved version, while still appearing cute and frilly on the "
"outside, actually conceals an advanced armor liner and climate control "
"systems to better endure even the harshest environments."
msgstr ""
"標準女僕制服可能不足以在這個危險的新世界中生存。這個改進版本，雖然外表仍然可愛且飾有褶邊，但實際上隱藏了先進的裝甲襯裡和氣候控制系統，以更好地承受最惡劣的環境。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO (on)"
msgid_plural "Cute Maid Uniform LSS-PRO (on)s"
msgstr[0] "可愛女僕制服 LSS-PRO（開啟）"

